{"word":"χράομαι","slug":"χράομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>χράομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χρή\">χρή</a></el>] a multivalent word like our ‘handle’<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘engage in making serviceable’, <b>use,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> <b><a href='B:510 27:17'>Ac 27:17</a>; <a href='B:530 9:12'>1 Cor 9:12</a>, <a href='B:530 9:15'>15</a>; <a href='B:610 1:8'>1 Ti 1:8</a>; <a href='B:610 5:23'>5:23</a>.</b> W. <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b>put to use <a href='B:530 7:31'>1 Cor 7:31</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘do <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> to meet a need in a situation’, <b>act <a href='B:540 1:17'>2 Cor 1:17</a>; <a href='B:540 3:12'>3:12</a>; <a href='B:540 13:10'>13:10</a>; function</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φιλανθρώπως\">φιλανθρώπως</a> χρῆσϑαι</el> function in a kindly manner or treat kindly, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χρηστός\">χρηστός</a></el>) <b><a href='B:510 27:3'>Ac 27:3</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μᾶλλον\">μᾶλλον</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χρῆσαι\">χρῆσαι</a></el> function all the more usefully, in sense of broadened opportunity if freed <b><a href='B:530 7:21'>1 Cor 7:21</a></b> (for other views see commentaries)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:χοῦς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:χράω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}